### =========================================================================
### PrimeFlux API E2E Integration Testing File (VS Code REST Client)
### =========================================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@contentType = application/json
@email = primeflux18@gmail.com
@phone = 0723456789

### 1. System Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 2. Register a New Customer User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "full_name": "Ken Eibba",
    "phone": "{{phone}}",
    "password": "SecurePassword123!",
    "role": "customer"
}

### 3. Register a New Driver User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "driver1@primeflux.com",
    "full_name": "John Driver",
    "phone": "0711223344",
    "password": "SecurePassword123!",
    "role": "driver",
    "national_id": "12345678",
    "license_number": "DL99382A"
}

### 4. Authenticate / Login (Saves Tokens Automatically)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "driver1@primeflux.com",
    "password": "SecurePassword123!"
}

### Capture tokens from login response
@accessToken = {{login.response.body.access}}
@refreshToken = {{login.response.body.refresh}}

### 5. Get Authenticated User Profile (Requires Login)
GET {{baseUrl}}/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: {{contentType}}

### 6. Update User Profile (Clears Redis Cache)
# @name updateProfile
PUT {{baseUrl}}/profile/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "full_name": "Ken Eibba Updated",
    "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

### 7. Send Phone OTP via Africa's Talking
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/phone/send/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "phone": "{{phone}}"
}

### 8. Verify Phone OTP & Activate Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/phone/verify/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "phone": "{{phone}}",
    "otp": "016955"
}

### 9. Send Email OTP via Resend
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/email/send/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "{{email}}"
}

### 10. Verify Email OTP & Activate Status
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/otp/email/verify/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "{{email}}",
    "otp": "553384"
}

### 11. Refresh Expired Access Token
# @name tokenRefresh
POST http://localhost:8000/api/v1/token/refresh/
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "refresh": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

### 12. Logout (Blacklist Refresh Token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout/
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "refresh": "{{refreshToken}}"
}
